{"tid":1732782,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"求下消防救護企出嚟救POLY","createTime":"2019-11-18T03:11:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T05:25:52.000Z","uid":295190,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e1b499a315114246c06da58f06227b9e357dfd9c","tid":1732782,"uid":295190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T03:11:22.000Z","msg":"而家已經困獸鬥喇<br />\n真槍都已經開咗唔少<br />\n普通市民而家無能力比到壓力政府喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我求下你地<br />\n<br />\n企出嚟喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家只可以靠你地同埋公職人員先有能力比到多啲壓力政府<br />\n如果你只係覺得一直都未係時候<br />\n而家就係喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你再唔企出嚟，企係學生前面<br />\n我地香港就會因為咁而白白無晒一代，甚至兩三代熱愛香港嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我已經受咗傷<br />\n今日已經無乜能力幫到大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望你地唔想我地白白斷送咗香港未來嘅就企出嚟喇<br />\n呢場運動如果輸埋<br />\n香港就會萬劫不復<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa2c045ba8c6d8b2e9b9e0c6f760c68fbdbb230a","tid":1732782,"uid":295190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T03:11:42.000Z","msg":"求下你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ae12cc088aba3d9886240ffb7b61dea4c7fd7c4","tid":1732782,"uid":295190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T03:12:04.000Z","msg":"求下消防員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6f6e6a34bbe908c7a67ce5d1bded0abdcef08ea","tid":1732782,"uid":295190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T03:12:19.000Z","msg":"救下救護<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69e2c815fc9e42b98d7b20d28c832e67f2bee747","tid":1732782,"uid":295190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T03:13:33.000Z","msg":"既然你見到政府嘅惡行<br />\n你地都一齊企出嚟做返香港人應該做嘅嘢喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.